{"tid":2428061,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"尋雞尾鸚鵡 呠呠囡","createTime":"2021-03-01T09:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:51:58.000Z","uid":390865,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a974c9f9be72ed1213bbd7a381d5184acce93737","tid":2428061,"uid":390865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫幫手留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地屋企真係好錫好錫呠呠<br />\n自從琴日走失咗之後  父親無咩點瞓過覺<br />\n由朝到晚一路叫呠呠一路行公園<br />\n或者推住架單車周圍走<br />\n我地成家人都請咗假去搵呠呠<br />\n4月1號就係呠呠4歲生日<br />\n希望可以同佢一齊過<br />\n麻煩大家幫幫手廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋雞尾鸚鵡<br />\n名：呠呠<br />\n地點：沙田沙角銀鷗樓附近<br />\n時間：28/2 下午5點20分左右<br />\n聯絡電話：<br />\n黃生 6171 0305<br />\n司徒 9466 6785<br />\n<br />\n有酬 謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMzO5qj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMzO5qj.jpg&h=54ee9bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCECYLo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCECYLo.png&h=b5e3dd37&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mN5ob8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mN5ob8.png&h=b6d63443&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruiHqqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FruiHqqx.png&h=dc6f199f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8JwaziX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8JwaziX.png&h=619efa97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZ8HqqG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZ8HqqG.png&h=679a272e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/woqiJcr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwoqiJcr.png&h=187773eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enH1FZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2